Armida (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Armida_(actress) 0 Armida, born Armida Vendrell, (29 May 1911 – 23 October 1989) was a Mexican actress, singer, dancer and vaudevillian born in Aguascalientes, Mexico.
